heading_19 = heading_15 + ">>(d) in the case of an action under the"
CONTEXT(heading_19, 'Fatal Accidents Act 1959 to be brought by a person under section 9(1) of that Act, means that person')
heading_20 = heading_15 + ">>(e) in the case of an action of a kind to which the"
CONTEXT(heading_20, 'Law Reform (Miscellaneous Provisions) Act 1941 section 4 applies, means either the deceased person or a personal representative of that person.')
heading_11 = heading_8 + ">>40. Court may extend time to commence defamation actions"
heading_12 = heading_11 + ">>(1)"
CONTEXT(heading_12, 'A plaintiff may apply to a court for leave to commence an action relating to the publication of defamatory matter even though one year has elapsed since the publication.')
heading_13 = heading_11 + ">>(2)"
CONTEXT(heading_13, 'Subject to subsection (3), on an application a court, if satisfied that it was not reasonable in the circumstances for the plaintiff to have commenced an action in relation to the matter complained of within one year from the publication, must extend the time in which the action can be commenced.')
heading_14 = heading_11 + ">>(3)"
CONTEXT(heading_14, 'An action relating to the publication of defamatory matter cannot be commenced if 3 years have elapsed since the publication.')
heading_12 = heading_8 + ">>41. Court may extend time to commence action by person under 18 when cause of action accrues, with guardian"
heading_13 = heading_12 + ">>(1)"
CONTEXT(heading_13, 'A plaintiff who was under 18 years of age when a cause of action accrued to that person may apply to a court for leave to commence an action even though the limitation period provided for under this Act has expired.')
heading_14 = heading_12 + ">>(2)"
CONTEXT(heading_14, 'Subject to subsection (3), on an application a court may extend the time in which the action can be commenced up to when the plaintiff reaches 21 years of age.')
heading_15 = heading_12 + ">>(3) A court is not to extend time on an application unless the court is satisfied that in the circumstances it was unreasonable for a"
CONTEXT(heading_15, 'guardian of the plaintiff not to commence the action within the limitation period for the action.')
heading_16 = heading_12 + ">>(4)"
CONTEXT(heading_16, 'This section does not apply to an action relating to the publication of defamatory matter.')
heading_13 = heading_8 + ">>42. Court may extend time to commence action by person with a mental disability, with guardian"
heading_14 = heading_13 + ">>(1)"
CONTEXT(heading_14, 'A plaintiff who suffers a mental disability at any time after a cause of action accrues to that person may apply to a court for leave to commence an action even though the limitation period provided for under this Act has expired.')
heading_15 = heading_13 + ">>(2)"
CONTEXT(heading_15, 'Subject to subsection (3), on an application a court may extend the time in which the action can be commenced up to 12 years from when the cause of action accrued.')
heading_16 = heading_13 + ">>(3)"
CONTEXT(heading_16, 'A court is not to extend time on an application unless the court is satisfied that in the circumstances it was unreasonable for a guardian of the plaintiff not to commence the action within the limitation period for the action.')
heading_17 = heading_13 + ">>(4)"
CONTEXT(heading_17, 'This section does not apply to an action relating to the publication of defamatory matter.')
heading_14 = heading_8 + ">>43. Jurisdiction and procedure"
heading_15 = heading_14 + ">>(1) Subject to subsection (2), an extension application is to be made by summons in the jurisdiction in which "
heading_16 = heading_15 + ">>a"
CONTEXT(heading_16, 'the existing action, if any, has been brought or')
heading_17 = heading_15 + ">>(b) the proposed action would be brought if the application were successful,"
CONTEXT(heading_17, 'as is relevant to the case.')
heading_16 = heading_14 + ">>(2)"
CONTEXT(heading_16, 'An extension application in respect of an arbitration for a difference or matter under an arbitration provision is to be made by summons to the Supreme Court.')
heading_17 = heading_14 + ">>(3)"
CONTEXT(heading_17, 'The plaintiff is to serve a copy of the summons on each person against whom the action that is the subject of the extension application is brought or proposed to be brought.')
heading_18 = heading_14 + ">>(4)"
CONTEXT(heading_18, 'Despite subsection (1), the Supreme Court may give leave to bring an action in any court which seems to it to be the appropriate court.')
heading_19 = heading_14 + ">>(5)"
CONTEXT(heading_19, 'An extension application can be sought or determined at any time before or after the issue, or close of, pleadings.')
heading_15 = heading_8 + ">>44. Further matters for courts consideration on extension applications; When deciding, on an extension application, whether to extend the time for the commencement of an action, a court is to have regard to "
heading_16 = heading_15 + ">>a"
CONTEXT(heading_16, 'whether the delay in commencing the proposed action, whatever the merit of the reasons for that delay, would unacceptably diminish the prospects of a fair trial of the action and')
heading_17 = heading_15 + ">>b"
CONTEXT(heading_17, 'whether extending the time would significantly prejudice the defendant (other than by reason only of the commencement of the proposed action).')
heading_9 = heading_5 + ">>Division 4  Extension or shortening by agreement"
heading_10 = heading_9 + ">>45. Agreement to extend or shorten limitation period"
heading_11 = heading_10 + ">>(1)"
CONTEXT(heading_11, 'Nothing in this Act prevents a person from agreeing to extend or shorten a limitation period provided for under this Act.')
heading_12 = heading_10 + ">>(2) Despite subsection (1), a provision in, or condition of, an agreement is of no effect if it purports to "
heading_13 = heading_12 + ">>a"
CONTEXT(heading_13, 'exclude the operation of section 33, 36 or 38 or')
heading_14 = heading_12 + ">>b"
CONTEXT(heading_14, 'extinguish (rather than bar) a right or title in relation to an action in a manner that would be inconsistent with a provision of Part 5.')
heading_10 = heading_5 + ">>Division 5  Extension by confirmation"
heading_11 = heading_10 + ">>46. Meaning of confirmation"
heading_12 = heading_11 + ">>(1) For the purposes of this Act, a person confirms a cause of action if the person "
heading_13 = heading_12 + ">>(a) acknowledges, to a person having the cause of action (person A"
CONTEXT(heading_13, '), person As right or title, even though the acknowledgment does not disclose a promise to pay')
heading_14 = heading_12 + ">>(b) makes, to a person having the cause of action (person B"
CONTEXT(heading_14, '), a payment in relation to person Bs right or title and makes the payment in circumstances not inconsistent with an acknowledgment of that right or title or')
heading_15 = heading_12 + ">>(c) makes, to a person having a cause of action to foreclose the equity of redemption of mortgaged property or to recover possession of mortgaged property (person C"
CONTEXT(heading_15, '), a payment of principal or interest secured by the mortgage or a payment to person C otherwise in relation to person Cs right or title to the mortgage.')
heading_13 = heading_11 + ">>(2)"
CONTEXT(heading_13, 'In subsection (1) a reference to a person having a cause of action is a reference to the person having the cause of action either solely or with other persons.')
heading_12 = heading_10 + ">>47. Limitation period extended by confirmation; If a cause of action lies against a person (either solely or with other persons) and the person confirms the cause of action "
heading_13 = heading_12 + ">>a"
CONTEXT(heading_13, 'after the limitation period provided for under this Act for the cause of action begins to run and')
heading_14 = heading_12 + ">>(b) before that limitation period expires,"
CONTEXT(heading_14, 'the time during which the limitation period runs before the confirmation is made does not count in the reckoning of the limitation period for an action on the cause of action by a person  having the benefit of the confirmation against a person bound by the confirmation.')
heading_13 = heading_10 + ">>48. Formal requirements for acknowledgments"
CONTEXT(heading_13, 'For the purposes of section 46(1)(a), an acknowledgment is of no effect unless it is in writing and signed by the maker.')
heading_14 = heading_10 + ">>49. Who has benefit of confirmation"
CONTEXT(heading_14, 'For the purposes of this Act, a person (person A ) has the benefit of a confirmation if the confirmation is made to person A or to a person through whom person A claims.')
heading_15 = heading_10 + ">>50. Who is bound by confirmation"
heading_16 = heading_15 + ">>(1) For the purposes of this Act, a person (person A"
heading_17 = heading_16 + ">>) is bound by a confirmation if "
heading_18 = heading_17 + ">>a"
CONTEXT(heading_18, 'person A is a maker of the confirmation')
heading_19 = heading_17 + ">>b"
CONTEXT(heading_19, 'person A is, in relation to the cause of action, a successor of a maker under a devolution from the maker occurring after the making of the confirmation')
heading_20 = heading_17 + ">>c"
CONTEXT(heading_20, 'in the case where the maker is, at the time when the maker makes the confirmation, a personal representative of a deceased person (either solely or with other persons)  person A is, at or after that time, a personal representative of the deceased person')
heading_21 = heading_17 + ">>d"
CONTEXT(heading_21, 'in the case where the maker is, at the time when the maker makes the confirmation, a trustee other than a personal representative of a deceased person (either solely or with other persons)  person A is, at or after that time, a trustee of the trust of which the maker is a trustee or')
heading_22 = heading_17 + ">>e"
CONTEXT(heading_22, 'person A is bound under subsection (2).')
heading_17 = heading_15 + ">>(2)"
CONTEXT(heading_17, 'If a maker of a confirmation of a cause of action in relation to property is in possession of the property when the confirmation is made, the confirmation binds a person subsequently in possession of the property who claims through the maker of the confirmation.')
heading_16 = heading_10 + ">>51. Effects of certain kinds of confirmation"
heading_17 = heading_16 + ">>(1)"
CONTEXT(heading_17, 'A confirmation of a cause of action to recover interest on principal money operates also as a confirmation of a cause of action to recover the principal money.')
heading_18 = heading_16 + ">>(2)"
CONTEXT(heading_18, 'A confirmation of a cause of action to recover income becoming due at any time operates also as a confirmation of a cause of action to recover income falling due at a later time on the same account.')
heading_11 = heading_5 + ">>Division 6  Extension of limitation periods  other matters"
heading_12 = heading_11 + ">>52. Persons with mental disability under 18 when cause of action accrues  most beneficial limitation period applies; If "
heading_13 = heading_12 + ">>a"
CONTEXT(heading_13, 'a person is under 18 years of age when a cause of action accrues to the person')
heading_14 = heading_12 + ">>b"
CONTEXT(heading_14, 'during any time after that time the person is suffering a mental disability and')
heading_15 = heading_12 + ">>(c) different limitation periods for commencing an action on the cause of action are provided for under section 7 or Division 1 or 2,"
CONTEXT(heading_15, 'the limitation period for commencing the action is the longer of those limitation periods.')
heading_13 = heading_11 + ">>53. Limitation period in case of death of certain persons if cause of action accrues to certain other persons"
heading_14 = heading_13 + ">>(1) In this section ; person A means "
heading_15 = heading_14 + ">>a"
CONTEXT(heading_15, 'a person who is under 18 years of age when a cause of action accrues to the person and who dies without having reached 18 years of age or')
heading_16 = heading_14 + ">>b"
CONTEXT(heading_16, 'a person who, at any time after a cause of action accrues to the person, is suffering a mental disability and who dies at a time when the person is suffering the mental disability.')
heading_15 = heading_13 + ">>(2) If, on person As death, person As cause of action accrues to a person (person B"
CONTEXT(heading_15, ') who is either under 18 years of age or suffering a mental disability when person A dies, a further extension of time is not allowed by reason of person Bs being under 18 years of age or suffering a mental disability.')
heading_14 = heading_11 + ">>54. Arbitration  extension of limitation period"
heading_15 = heading_14 + ">>(1) If a court "
heading_16 = heading_15 + ">>a"
CONTEXT(heading_16, 'removes an arbitrator or umpire')
heading_17 = heading_15 + ">>b"
CONTEXT(heading_17, 'restrains a party or an arbitrator or umpire from proceeding with an arbitration or')
heading_18 = heading_15 + ">>(c) sets aside an arbitral award,"
CONTEXT(heading_18, 'the court may at the same time or within 6 months afterwards, whether or not the limitation period provided for under this Act for commencing an action with respect to the difference or matter under arbitration has expired, order that the whole or any part of the time between the commencement of the arbitration and the making of the order under this section does not count in the reckoning of the limitation period.')
heading_16 = heading_14 + ">>(2)"
CONTEXT(heading_16, 'If, after the expiration of a limitation period provided for under this Act, a court makes an order under this section, the expiration of the first limitation period has no effect for the purposes of this Act.')
heading_6 = heading_2 + ">>Part 4  Accrual of particular causes of action"
heading_7 = heading_6 + ">>Division 1  Accrual of certain causes of action other than to recover land"
heading_8 = heading_7 + ">>55. Personal injury  general"
heading_9 = heading_8 + ">>(1) A cause of action for damages relating to a personal injury to a person accrues when the only or earlier of such of the following events as are applicable occurs "
heading_10 = heading_9 + ">>a"
CONTEXT(heading_10, 'the person becomes aware that he or she has sustained a not insignificant personal injury')
heading_11 = heading_9 + ">>b"
CONTEXT(heading_11, 'the first symptom, clinical sign or other manifestation of personal injury consistent with the person having sustained a not insignificant personal injury.')
heading_10 = heading_8 + ">>(2) This section does not apply to a personal injury that is attributable to the inhalation of asbestos or silica dust."
CONTEXT(heading_10, '[Section 55 amended No. 21 of 2023 s. 656.]')
heading_9 = heading_7 + ">>56. Asbestos or silica dust related diseases"
heading_10 = heading_9 + ">>(1) A cause of action for damages relating to a personal injury "
heading_11 = heading_10 + ">>a"
CONTEXT(heading_11, 'that is attributable to the inhalation of asbestos or silica dust and')
heading_12 = heading_10 + ">>(b) to a person who did not have knowledge of the relevant facts before 1 January 1984,"
CONTEXT(heading_12, 'accrues when the person has knowledge of the relevant facts.')
heading_11 = heading_9 + ">>(2) For the purposes of this section a person has knowledge of the relevant facts in relation to a cause of action when the person has knowledge "
heading_12 = heading_11 + ">>a"
CONTEXT(heading_12, 'that the injury in question was significant')
heading_13 = heading_11 + ">>b"
CONTEXT(heading_13, 'that the injury was attributable in whole or in part to the act or omission which is alleged to constitute the cause of action')
heading_14 = heading_11 + ">>c"
CONTEXT(heading_14, 'of the identity of the defendant and')
heading_15 = heading_11 + ">>(d) if it is alleged that the act or omission was that of a person other than the defendant, of the identity of that person and the additional facts supporting the bringing of an action against the defendant,"
CONTEXT(heading_15, 'and knowledge that any acts or omissions did or did not, as a matter of law, give rise to a cause of action is irrelevant.')
heading_12 = heading_9 + ">>(3)"
CONTEXT(heading_12, 'For the purposes of this section an injury is significant if the person whose knowledge is in question would reasonably have considered it sufficiently serious to justify the persons commencing an action for damages against a defendant who did not dispute liability and was able to satisfy a judgment.')
heading_13 = heading_9 + ">>(4) For the purposes of this section an injury to which this subsection applies must not be treated as significant unless "
heading_14 = heading_13 + ">>a"
CONTEXT(heading_14, 'the parties to the proposed action have so agreed or')
heading_15 = heading_13 + ">>(b) a medical panel constituted as described in the; Workers Compensation and Injury Management Act 1981 section 36(1) "
heading_16 = heading_15 + ">>(i) has determined that the degree of the disability assessed in accordance with section 93D(2) of that Act is 30% or more or"
heading_17 = heading_16 + ">>(ii) has assessed that the workers degree of whole of person impairment evaluated as described in sections 146A and 146C of that Act (on or after 14 November 2005) is 25% or more"
CONTEXT(heading_17, 'or')
heading_16 = heading_13 + ">>(c) a Dust Disease Medical Panel constituted under the"
heading_17 = heading_16 + ">>Workers Compensation and Injury Management Act 2023 section 124 has determined for the purposes of Part 7 Division 2 of that Act that the degree of permanent whole of person impairment resulting from the injury is at least 25%.; (4A) Subsection (4) applies to an injury that "
heading_18 = heading_17 + ">>(a) before 14 November 2005, is a disability as defined in the"
heading_19 = heading_18 + ">>heading1"
CONTEXT(heading_19, 'Workers Compensation and Injury Management Act 1981 or')
heading_19 = heading_17 + ">>(b) on or after 14 November 2005 and before the commencement of the"
heading_20 = heading_19 + ">>heading1"
CONTEXT(heading_20, 'Workers Compensation and Injury Management Act 2023 Part 7 Division 2, is an injury as defined in the')
heading_21 = heading_19 + ">>heading2"
CONTEXT(heading_21, 'Workers Compensation and Injury Management Act 1981 or')
heading_20 = heading_17 + ">>c"
CONTEXT(heading_20, 'on or after the commencement of the')
heading_18 = heading_16 + ">>content2"
CONTEXT(heading_18, 'Workers Compensation and Injury Management Act 2023 Part 7 Division 2, is an injury from employment for the purposes of that Act.')
heading_14 = heading_9 + ">>(5) For the purposes of this section a persons knowledge includes knowledge which the person might reasonably have been expected to acquire "
heading_15 = heading_14 + ">>a"
CONTEXT(heading_15, 'from facts observable or ascertainable by the person or')
heading_16 = heading_14 + ">>(b) from facts ascertainable by the person with the help of medical or other appropriate expert advice which it is reasonable for the person to seek,"
heading_17 = heading_16 + ">>but a person is not to be fixed under this subsection with knowledge of a fact ascertainable only with the help of expert advice so long as the person has taken all reasonable steps to obtain (and, where appropriate, to act on) that advice."
CONTEXT(heading_17, '[Section 56 amended No. 21 of 2023 s. 657.]')
heading_10 = heading_7 + ">>57. Survival of certain actions"
heading_11 = heading_10 + ">>(1)"
CONTEXT(heading_11, 'If a person dies as a result of a personal injury other than an injury that is attributable to the inhalation of asbestos or silica dust but, immediately before the death, a cause of action relating to the personal injury had not accrued under section 55, the cause of action relating to the personal injury is to be taken as having accrued when the person died.')
heading_12 = heading_10 + ">>(2) If a person dies as a result of a personal injury that is attributable to the inhalation of asbestos or silica dust but, immediately before the death, a cause of action relating to the personal injury had not accrued under section 56, the cause of action relating to the personal injury is to be taken as having accrued when the person died."
CONTEXT(heading_12, '[Section 57 amended No. 21 of 2023 s. 658.]')
heading_11 = heading_7 + ">>58. Contributions between tortfeasors; A cause of action for contribution under the  Law Reform (Contributory Negligence and Tortfeasors Contribution) Act 1947 section 7 accrues to a person (person A ) "
heading_12 = heading_11 + ">>a"
CONTEXT(heading_12, 'in the case where person A is liable in respect of the damage for which contribution is claimed by judgment of a court or by arbitral award  when the judgment is given or the award is made, whether or not, in the case of a judgment, the judgment is afterwards varied as to quantum of damages or')
heading_13 = heading_11 + ">>b"
CONTEXT(heading_13, 'in any other case, if person A makes an agreement with a person having a cause of action for the damage for which the cause of action for contribution arises, which agreement fixes, as between the parties to the agreement, the amount of the liability in respect of the damage of person A or a person through whom person A claims  when the agreement is made.')
heading_12 = heading_7 + ">>59. Debts repayable on demand"
CONTEXT(heading_12, 'A cause of action for the repayment of a debt repayable on demand accrues when there is a failure to comply with a demand for repayment.')
heading_13 = heading_7 + ">>60. Successive wrongs to goods; If "
heading_14 = heading_13 + ">>a"
CONTEXT(heading_14, 'a cause of action for the conversion or detention of goods accrues to a person')
heading_15 = heading_13 + ">>b"
CONTEXT(heading_15, 'possession of the goods is not recovered by the person or by a person claiming through the person and')
heading_16 = heading_13 + ">>(c) a further cause of action for the conversion or detention of the goods or a cause of action to recover the proceeds of sale of the goods accrues to the person or to a person claiming through the person,"
CONTEXT(heading_16, 'the cause of action for the further conversion or detention or to recover the proceeds of sale accrues when the cause of action mentioned in paragraph (a) accrues.')
heading_14 = heading_7 + ">>61. Equitable interests"
CONTEXT(heading_14, 'A cause of action to enforce an equitable estate or interest in land accrues, for the purposes of this Act, in the same manner and circumstances as, and when, a cause of action to recover the land would accrue if the estate or interest were a legal estate or interest.')
heading_15 = heading_7 + ">>62. Future interests of beneficiaries under trusts"
CONTEXT(heading_15, 'A cause of action of a beneficiary relating to a future interest in trust property accrues when the beneficiary becomes entitled to immediate possession of the property.')
heading_16 = heading_7 + ">>63. Matters referable to arbitration; If, under an arbitration provision, a cause of action with respect to any difference or matter referable to arbitration under the arbitration provision "
heading_17 = heading_16 + ">>a"
CONTEXT(heading_17, 'does not accrue until the making of an arbitral award or the happening of some other event in or relating to the arbitration or')
heading_18 = heading_16 + ">>(b) does not accrue at all,"
CONTEXT(heading_18, 'the cause of action nevertheless accrues, for the purposes of the application of this Act to an arbitration under the arbitration provision, when it would have accrued but for that arbitration provision.')
heading_17 = heading_7 + ">>64. Arbitral awards"
CONTEXT(heading_17, 'A cause of action to enforce an arbitral award accrues when default in observance of the award first occurs, being the default in respect of which the action is brought.')
heading_8 = heading_6 + ">>Division 2  Accrual of certain causes of action to recover land"
heading_9 = heading_8 + ">>65. Adverse possession"
heading_10 = heading_9 + ">>(1)"
CONTEXT(heading_10, 'A cause of action to recover land does not accrue unless the land is in adverse possession and if, under this Act, such a cause of action would have accrued at a certain time but the land is not in adverse possession at that time, the cause of action does not accrue unless and until adverse possession of the land is taken.')
heading_11 = heading_9 + ">>(2) Subject to subsection (3), if "
heading_12 = heading_11 + ">>a"
CONTEXT(heading_12, 'a cause of action accrues to recover land from a person in adverse possession of the land and')
heading_13 = heading_11 + ">>(b) afterwards, the land is in the adverse possession of a second person, whether the second person claims through the first person or not,"
CONTEXT(heading_13, 'the cause of action to recover the land from the second person accrues when the cause of action mentioned in paragraph (a) accrues.')
heading_12 = heading_9 + ">>(3)"
CONTEXT(heading_12, 'If a cause of action to recover land accrues and afterwards, but before the limitation period for the action expires, the land ceases to be in adverse possession, the cause of action does not accrue unless and until adverse possession of the land is taken again.')
heading_10 = heading_8 + ">>66. Dispossession or discontinuance"
CONTEXT(heading_10, 'A cause of action to recover land by a person who has been in possession of the land and, while entitled to the land, is dispossessed or discontinues possession, accrues when the person is dispossessed, or discontinues the possession.')
heading_11 = heading_8 + ">>67. Deceased in possession; A cause of action to recover the land of a deceased person (whether under a will or on intestacy) accrues when the deceased died if, at that time, the deceased was "
heading_12 = heading_11 + ">>a"
CONTEXT(heading_12, 'in possession of the land, or in the case of a rentcharge created by will or taking effect upon the deceaseds death, in possession of the land charged and')
heading_13 = heading_11 + ">>b"
CONTEXT(heading_13, 'the last person entitled to the land to be in possession of the land.')
heading_12 = heading_8 + ">>68. Grantor in possession; A cause of action to recover a persons land being an estate or interest assured as an estate or interest in possession (otherwise than by will) to the person, accrues when the assurance takes effect if "
heading_13 = heading_12 + ">>a"
CONTEXT(heading_13, 'when the assurance takes effect, the person making the assurance is in possession under the estate or interest claimed or under an estate or interest out of which the assurance is made and')
heading_14 = heading_12 + ">>b"
CONTEXT(heading_14, 'after the time the assurance takes effect and before the action is commenced, no person is in possession under the estate or interest claimed and under the assurance.')
heading_13 = heading_8 + ">>69. Future interests in land"
heading_14 = heading_13 + ">>(1) A cause of action to recover land in which a person has a future interest accrues when the person becomes entitled to immediate possession of the land if, after the person becomes so entitled"
CONTEXT(heading_14, 'and before the action is commenced, no person is in possession under the interest claimed.')
heading_15 = heading_13 + ">>(2)"
CONTEXT(heading_15, 'Subsection (1) is subject to section 77.')
heading_14 = heading_8 + ">>70. Forfeiture; Subject to section 71, if "
heading_15 = heading_14 + ">>a"
CONTEXT(heading_15, 'a cause of action, arising from a forfeiture, to recover land accrues to a person who has a future interest in the land and')
heading_16 = heading_14 + ">>(b) neither the person nor a person claiming under the person recovers the land,"
CONTEXT(heading_16, 'a fresh cause of action to recover the land accrues to a person who becomes entitled to immediate possession of the land when that person becomes so entitled.')
heading_15 = heading_8 + ">>71. Rent wrongly paid; If "
heading_16 = heading_15 + ">>a"
CONTEXT(heading_16, 'a tenant is in possession of land under a lease for a term reserving a rent amounting to a yearly sum of not less than $2.00')
heading_17 = heading_15 + ">>b"
CONTEXT(heading_17, 'the rent is received by a person wrongfully claiming to be entitled to the land subject to the lease and')
heading_18 = heading_15 + ">>(c) no rent is afterwards received by the landlord and in consequence the lease can be determined,"
CONTEXT(heading_18, 'the cause of action of the landlord to recover the land from a person mentioned in paragraph (a) or (b) or from a person claiming under such a person accrues at the earliest time when the lease can be determined.')
heading_16 = heading_8 + ">>72. Tenancies"
heading_17 = heading_16 + ">>(1) A cause of action of a person entitled to land subject to a periodic tenancy to recover the land from the tenant or from a; person claiming under the tenant accrues when the only or later of such of the following events as are applicable occurs "
heading_18 = heading_17 + ">>a"
CONTEXT(heading_18, 'the first year or other period of the tenancy expires')
heading_19 = heading_17 + ">>b"
CONTEXT(heading_19, 'if the tenancy is at a rent  the rent payable to the person having the cause of action or a person through whom the person claims first becomes overdue.')
heading_18 = heading_16 + ">>(2) A cause of action of a person entitled to land subject to a tenancy at will to recover the land from the tenant or from a person claiming under the tenant accrues when the only or later of such of the following events as are applicable occurs "
heading_19 = heading_18 + ">>a"
CONTEXT(heading_19, 'the first year of the tenancy expires')
heading_20 = heading_18 + ">>b"
CONTEXT(heading_20, 'if the tenancy is at a rentthe rent payable to the person having the cause of action or a person through whom the person claims first becomes overdue.')
heading_19 = heading_16 + ">>(3)"
CONTEXT(heading_19, 'Subsection (1) or (2), as is applicable in the case, does not apply if the cause of action accrues earlier because the tenancy is determined.')
heading_17 = heading_8 + ">>73. Beneficial co-owners of land"
heading_18 = heading_17 + ">>(1) In this section "
heading_19 = heading_18 + ">>content1"
CONTEXT(heading_19, 'land means land held on trust under a settlement')
heading_20 = heading_18 + ">>content2"
CONTEXT(heading_20, 'settlement means a disposition, inter vivos or by will, of property upon trust, where no person is, immediately after the disposition takes effect, beneficially entitled to the trust property absolutely.')
heading_19 = heading_17 + ">>(2)"
CONTEXT(heading_19, 'A cause of action to recover land that is in the possession of a person entitled under the settlement to immediate possession of the land does not, for the purposes of this Act, accrue during such possession to the trustee or any other person entitled to an estate or interest in the land under the settlement.')
heading_20 = heading_17 + ">>(3) Subsection (2) does not apply to a cause of action against "
heading_21 = heading_20 + ">>a"
CONTEXT(heading_21, 'a person in possession who is solely and absolutely entitled under the settlement to the land or')
heading_22 = heading_20 + ">>b"
CONTEXT(heading_22, '2 or more persons in possession who are absolutely entitled under the settlement to the land as joint tenants or as tenants in common.')
heading_7 = heading_2 + ">>Part 5  Effect of expiration of limitation period"
heading_8 = heading_7 + ">>74. Time to commence actions may be extended despite extinguishment of rights; Nothing in this Part prevents "
heading_9 = heading_8 + ">>a"
CONTEXT(heading_9, 'a person from making an application under section 38, 41 or 42 for leave to commence an action to recover land or')
heading_10 = heading_8 + ">>(b) a court, on such an application, from extending the time in which an action to recover land can be commenced,"
CONTEXT(heading_10, 'even though the limitation period provided for under this Act has expired.')
heading_9 = heading_7 + ">>75. Extinguishment of right and title to land; A persons right and title to land is extinguished "
heading_10 = heading_9 + ">>a"
CONTEXT(heading_10, 'if the person does not commence an action to recover the land before the expiry of the limitation period provided for under this Act or')
heading_11 = heading_9 + ">>(b) if "
heading_12 = heading_11 + ">>(i) a court extends the time in which the person can commence an action to recover the land and"
CONTEXT(heading_12, '(ii) the person does not commence an action to recover the land before the expiry of the extended period.')
heading_10 = heading_7 + ">>76. No title by adverse possession against Crown"
CONTEXT(heading_10, 'Despite any law that is, or has been, in effect the right, title or interest of the Crown to, or in, any land is not affected in any way by any possession of such land adverse to the Crown, and is to be taken as never having been so affected.')
heading_11 = heading_7 + ">>77. Future interests in land"
heading_12 = heading_11 + ">>(1) If "
heading_13 = heading_12 + ">>a"
CONTEXT(heading_13, 'a persons right to the immediate possession of land is extinguished by this Act')
heading_14 = heading_12 + ">>b"
CONTEXT(heading_14, 'at any time while the person has that right the person also has a future interest in the land and')
heading_15 = heading_12 + ">>(c) the land is not, before the person becomes entitled to immediate possession of the land, recovered under an intervening interest,"
CONTEXT(heading_15, 'the future interest is extinguished when the person becomes entitled to immediate possession of the land.')
heading_13 = heading_11 + ">>(2) For the purposes of this section, a person has a future interest if "
heading_14 = heading_13 + ">>a"
CONTEXT(heading_14, 'the person is contingently entitled to a future interest or')
heading_15 = heading_13 + ">>b"
CONTEXT(heading_15, 'a future interest is vested in the person subject to divesting in any event.')
heading_12 = heading_7 + ">>78. Provisions in case of land held on trust"
heading_13 = heading_12 + ">>(1) If land is held upon trust including a trust for sale and "
heading_14 = heading_13 + ">>a"
CONTEXT(heading_14, 'the limitation period for an action by the trustee to recover the land has expired or')
heading_15 = heading_13 + ">>(b) a court extends the time in which the trustee can commence an action to recover the land and the trustee does not commence an action to recover the land before the expiry of the extended period,"
CONTEXT(heading_15, 'the estate of the trustee is not extinguished so long as the right of action to recover the land of any person entitled to a beneficial interest in the land or in the proceeds of sale either has not accrued or has not been barred by this Act but if every such right of action has been so barred the estate of the trustee is extinguished.')
heading_14 = heading_12 + ">>(2)"
CONTEXT(heading_14, 'If land is held upon trust including a trust for sale, an action to recover the land may be brought by the trustee on behalf of any person entitled to a beneficial interest in possession in the land or in the proceeds of sale whose right of action has not been barred by this Act even though the right of action of the trustee would apart from this provision have been barred by this Act.')
heading_8 = heading_2 + ">>Part 6  Miscellaneous"
heading_9 = heading_8 + ">>79. Burden of proof"
heading_10 = heading_9 + ">>(1)"
CONTEXT(heading_10, 'Subject to subsection (2), a defendant in an action has the burden of proving that the action cannot be commenced because the applicable limitation period has expired.')
heading_11 = heading_9 + ">>(2)"
CONTEXT(heading_11, 'The plaintiff has the burden of proving that the time mentioned in section 32(1) or 35(1) does not count in the reckoning of the limitation period.')
heading_12 = heading_9 + ">>(3)"
CONTEXT(heading_12, 'The plaintiff in an extension application has the burden of proving that a court should extend the relevant limitation period.')
heading_10 = heading_8 + ">>80. Grounds in equity upon which to refuse relief preserved"
CONTEXT(heading_10, 'Nothing in this Act affects any equitable jurisdiction to refuse relief on the ground of laches, acquiescence or otherwise.')
heading_11 = heading_8 + ">>81. Counterclaims  commencement"
heading_12 = heading_11 + ">>(1)"
CONTEXT(heading_12, 'A counterclaim in an action (except a counterclaim solely by way of defence) is, for the purposes of this Act, a separate action.')
heading_13 = heading_11 + ">>(2)"
CONTEXT(heading_13, 'If a defendant in an action makes a counterclaim against a plaintiff in the action the counterclaim is to be taken to have commenced as against the plaintiff when the defendant became a party to the action.')
heading_14 = heading_11 + ">>(3)"
CONTEXT(heading_14, 'If a defendant in an action makes a counterclaim against a plaintiff in the action and then joins another person as a party against whom the counterclaim is made the counterclaim is to be taken to have commenced as against the other person when the other person is joined as a party to the counterclaim.')
heading_12 = heading_8 + ">>82. Joint causes of action"
CONTEXT(heading_12, 'If, were it not for this Act, 2 or more persons would have a cause of action jointly but, because of this Act, an action on the  cause of action cannot be commenced by one or more of them, an action on the cause of action may nonetheless be commenced by the other or others of them and judgment may be given accordingly.')
heading_13 = heading_8 + ">>83. Joint liability"
CONTEXT(heading_13, 'If, were it not for this Act, 2 or more persons would be liable on a cause of action jointly but, because of this Act, an action on the cause of action cannot be commenced against one or more of them, an action on the cause of action may nonetheless be commenced against the other or others of them and judgment may be given accordingly.')
heading_14 = heading_8 + ">>84. Formal entry and claim; For the purposes of this Act "
heading_15 = heading_14 + ">>a"
CONTEXT(heading_15, 'a formal entry on land is not of itself possession or evidence of possession of the land and')
heading_16 = heading_14 + ">>b"
CONTEXT(heading_16, 'a claim in respect of land does not preserve a cause of action to recover the land.')
heading_15 = heading_8 + ">>85. Other beneficiaries"
CONTEXT(heading_15, 'If a beneficiary under a trust brings an action in relation to the trust (beneficiary 1s action ), any other beneficiary under the trust (beneficiary 2 ) is not entitled to derive from beneficiary 1s action any benefit for which, because of this Act, beneficiary 2 could not have commenced an action when beneficiary 1s action was commenced.')
heading_16 = heading_8 + ">>86. Limited right to recover tax"
heading_17 = heading_16 + ">>(1) This section applies in respect of an action by a person (a claimant"
CONTEXT(heading_17, ') to recover, or in relation to the recovery of, any money paid by way of tax or purported tax.')
heading_18 = heading_16 + ">>(2) Any judgment by a court in favour of a claimant is to be for only that part of the amount claimed which the court is satisfied "
heading_19 = heading_18 + ">>a"
CONTEXT(heading_19, 'has not been charged directly to or recovered directly from another person or, if it has been so charged or recovered, has been refunded to the other person')
heading_20 = heading_18 + ">>b"
CONTEXT(heading_20, 'will not be charged directly to or recovered directly from another person and')
heading_21 = heading_18 + ">>c"
CONTEXT(heading_21, 'has not been incorporated into the price of or charge for any property or services.')
heading_19 = heading_16 + ">>(3)"
CONTEXT(heading_19, 'The claimant has the burden of satisfying the court as to the matters mentioned in subsection (2).')
heading_17 = heading_8 + ">>87. Limited operation of certain court orders as to refund of tax"
heading_18 = heading_17 + ">>(1)"
CONTEXT(heading_18, 'This section applies when the effect of an order of a court (other than a judgment mentioned in section 86(2)) is to oblige a taxing authority to refund any money paid by way of tax or purported tax.')
heading_19 = heading_17 + ">>(2) A taxing authority is to refund only that part of a tax or purported tax which the taxing authority is satisfied "
heading_20 = heading_19 + ">>a"
CONTEXT(heading_20, 'has not been charged directly to or recovered directly from another person or, if it has been so charged or recovered, has been refunded to the other person')
heading_21 = heading_19 + ">>b"
CONTEXT(heading_21, 'will not be charged directly to or recovered directly from another person and')
heading_22 = heading_19 + ">>c"
CONTEXT(heading_22, 'has not been incorporated into the price of or charge for any property or services.')
heading_20 = heading_17 + ">>(3)"
CONTEXT(heading_20, 'The person to whom the refund is to be made has the burden of satisfying a taxing authority as to the matters mentioned in subsection (2).')
heading_21 = heading_17 + ">>(4) In this section "
CONTEXT(heading_21, 'taxing authority means a person who or which under an Act is responsible for the assessment or collection of any tax.')
heading_18 = heading_8 + ">>88. Arbitrations  commencement"
heading_19 = heading_18 + ">>(1) For the purposes of this Act "
heading_20 = heading_19 + ">>(a) if an arbitration provision requires or permits a party to the arbitration to give notice in writing to another party "
heading_21 = heading_20 + ">>(i) requiring the other party to appoint or concur in appointing an arbitrator or"
heading_22 = heading_21 + ">>(ii) requiring the other party to submit or concur in submitting a difference or matter to a person named or designated in the provisions for arbitration as arbitrator"
CONTEXT(heading_22, 'or')
heading_21 = heading_19 + ">>(b) if, in a case to which paragraph (a) does not apply, a party to the arbitration takes a step required or permitted by an arbitration provision for the purpose of bringing a difference or matter before an arbitrator and gives to another party notice in writing of the taking of the step,"
CONTEXT(heading_21, 'the arbitration is to be taken to have commenced, as between the party giving the notice and the party to whom the notice is given, when the notice is given.')
heading_20 = heading_18 + ">>(2) For the purpose of subsection (1), a notice is given when the notice is given "
heading_21 = heading_20 + ">>(a) in accordance with the"
heading_22 = heading_21 + ">>heading1"
CONTEXT(heading_22, 'Interpretation Act 1984 section 76 or')
heading_22 = heading_20 + ">>(b) in a manner required or permitted by the provisions for arbitration,"
CONTEXT(heading_22, 'whichever occurs first.')
heading_9 = heading_2 + ">>Part 7  Transitional provisions  [Heading inserted No. 3 of 2018 s. 12.]"
heading_10 = heading_9 + ">>Division 1  Provisions for Civil Liability Legislation Amendment (Child Sexual Abuse Actions) Act 2018  [Heading inserted No. 3 of 2018 s. 12.]"
heading_11 = heading_10 + ">>89. Terms used; In this Division "
heading_12 = heading_11 + ">>content1"
CONTEXT(heading_12, 'child sexual abuse has the meaning given in section 6A(1)')
heading_13 = heading_11 + ">>content2"
CONTEXT(heading_13, 'child sexual abuse action has the meaning given in section 6A(1)')
heading_14 = heading_11 + ">>content3"
CONTEXT(heading_14, 'child sexual abuse cause of action has the meaning given in section 6A(1)')
heading_15 = heading_11 + ">>content4"
CONTEXT(heading_15, 'commencement day means the day on which the  Civil Liability Legislation Amendment (Child Sexual Abuse Actions) Act 2018 section 12 comes into operation')
heading_16 = heading_11 + ">>content5"
CONTEXT(heading_16, 'previously barred cause of action means a child sexual abuse cause of action that was statute barred immediately before commencement day')
heading_17 = heading_11 + ">>content6"
CONTEXT(heading_17, 'previously settled cause of action means a child sexual abuse cause of action that was settled after it was statute barred but before commencement day')
heading_18 = heading_11 + ">>statute barred, in relation to a child sexual abuse cause of action, means that action on the cause of action cannot be maintained "
heading_19 = heading_18 + ">>a"
CONTEXT(heading_19, 'under one of the provisions referred to in section 6A(3) or')
heading_20 = heading_18 + ">>(b) because a limitation period applicable to the action under this or any other Act has expired."
CONTEXT(heading_20, '[Section 89 inserted No. 3 of 2018 s. 12.]')
heading_12 = heading_10 + ">>90. Application of section 6A"
heading_13 = heading_12 + ">>Section 6A applies in relation to a child sexual abuse action regardless of when the act or omission constituting child sexual abuse occurred."
CONTEXT(heading_13, '[Section 90 inserted No. 3 of 2018 s. 12.]')
heading_13 = heading_10 + ">>91. Previously barred causes of action"
heading_14 = heading_13 + ">>(1) An action on a previously barred cause of action may be commenced even though one or more of the following apply "
heading_15 = heading_14 + ">>a"
CONTEXT(heading_15, 'the action was statute barred before commencement day')
heading_16 = heading_14 + ">>b"
CONTEXT(heading_16, 'an action on the cause of action had commenced but was discontinued or not finalised before commencement day')
heading_17 = heading_14 + ">>c"
CONTEXT(heading_17, 'a judgment was given before commencement day in relation to the cause of action on the ground that the action was statute barred')
heading_18 = heading_14 + ">>d"
CONTEXT(heading_18, 'an action on the cause of action was dismissed before commencement day on the ground that the action was statute barred.')
heading_15 = heading_13 + ">>(2) Application may be made to a court with jurisdiction to deal with the action to set aside a judgment referred to in subsection (1)(c) or (d) (the previous judgment"
CONTEXT(heading_15, '). An application may be made prior to the commencement of the action.')
heading_16 = heading_13 + ">>(3)"
CONTEXT(heading_16, 'The court may, if satisfied that it is just and reasonable to do so, set aside the previous judgment to the extent to which it relates to the action.')
heading_17 = heading_13 + ">>(4)"
CONTEXT(heading_17, 'If the previous judgment is wholly or partly set aside, a person who paid an amount under the judgment cannot seek to recover that amount on the basis of the judgment having been set aside to that extent.')
heading_18 = heading_13 + ">>(5) If an action on a previously barred cause of action is commenced, the court dealing with the action may, if satisfied that it is just and reasonable to do so, take into account any"
CONTEXT(heading_18, 'amount paid under a previous judgment relating to the cause of action.')
heading_19 = heading_13 + ">>(6) A court, other than the Supreme Court, may not set aside a previous judgment of another court."
CONTEXT(heading_19, '[Section 91 inserted No. 3 of 2018 s. 12.]')
heading_14 = heading_10 + ">>92. Previously settled causes of action"
heading_15 = heading_14 + ">>(1) This section applies in relation to a proposed action on a previously settled cause of action and to the agreement effecting the settlement (the settlement agreement"
CONTEXT(heading_15, ').')
heading_16 = heading_14 + ">>(2)"
CONTEXT(heading_16, 'Application may be made to a court that would have jurisdiction to deal with the action, but for the settlement agreement, for leave to commence the action.')
heading_17 = heading_14 + ">>(3) The court may, if satisfied that it is just and reasonable to do so "
heading_18 = heading_17 + ">>a"
CONTEXT(heading_18, 'grant leave to commence the action, subject to conditions and')
heading_19 = heading_17 + ">>b"
CONTEXT(heading_19, 'to the extent necessary for that, set aside the settlement agreement and any judgment giving effect to the settlement.')
heading_18 = heading_14 + ">>(4)"
CONTEXT(heading_18, 'If an action on the previously settled cause of action is commenced, the settlement agreement and each agreement relating to the settlement, other than a contract of insurance, is, despite any written or other law, void to the extent to which it relates to the child sexual abuse the subject of the cause of action.')
heading_19 = heading_14 + ">>(5)"
CONTEXT(heading_19, 'A party to an agreement that is wholly or partly void under subsection (4) cannot seek to recover an amount paid by or for the party under the agreement on the basis that the agreement is void to that extent.')
heading_20 = heading_14 + ">>(6) The court dealing with the action may, if satisfied that it is just and reasonable to do so, take into account any amount paid"
CONTEXT(heading_20, 'under an agreement that is wholly or partly void under this section, to the extent to which the amount relates to the child sexual abuse the subject of the cause of action.')
heading_21 = heading_14 + ">>(7) For the purposes of subsection (6), amounts paid under an agreement are taken to relate to the child sexual abuse the subject of the cause of action to the extent of 50% if the agreement "
heading_22 = heading_21 + ">>a"
CONTEXT(heading_22, 'does not relate solely to that child sexual abuse and')
heading_23 = heading_21 + ">>(b) does not expressly deal with the extent to which the agreement and amounts paid under it relate to that child sexual abuse.; [Section 92 inserted No. 3 of 2018 s. 12.]"
heading_24 = heading_23 + ">>Notes"
CONTEXT(heading_24, 'This is a compilation of the  Limitation Act 2005 and includes amendments made by other written laws. For provisions that have come into operation see the compilation table.')
